# Office-doc exports from AI skills (code reviews, design docs,
# meeting notes, etc.) — these get created as throwaway outputs
# at the repo root and should never be checked in. Source of
# truth for any decisions captured this way lives in commit
# messages, ADRs under docs/, or the issue tracker.
*.docx
*.pptx
*.xlsx
*.odt
*.ods
*.odp
